oai_dc:dc.dc:title: FIELD STUDY ON WAVE RUN-UP ON SEADYKES
oai_dc:dc.dc:creator: Grune, Joachim
oai_dc:dc.dc:subject: field study
run up
dike
oai_dc:dc.dc:description: This paper deals with a comprehensive field research program on wave runup, which is ongoing at different locations at the landside borders of the wadden sea (tidal flats ) and the tidal estuaries of the German Bight since 1991. The field measurement equipment is described and an overview about first results is given.
oai_dc:dc.dc:source: Coastal Engineering Proceedings; No. 25 (1996): Proceedings of 25th Conference on Coastal Engineering, Orlando, Florida, 1996.
